{
  "stem": "18581.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 322.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a priest and a professor of bibliography.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It says [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is advisable quickly to change your living quarters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you will have some difficulties-- [NON-ENGLISH] and this address.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If there will be some difficulties, please contact the priest Gediminas Peletskis And they gave the address.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I forgot the address.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I tried when I was after the war in '91 or '92 in Vilna to get his address and his details from the curia.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they did not have the documents, because the Russians have confiscated in the '80s all the archives of the-- of the bishop in Vilna, probably in all of Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were separated-- the shooting, my friend and I, and we-- we-- we got there separately.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't know all the time about my friend that he was alive, because the priest, although he was not trained in intelligence, knew very well how to separate things, was very smart.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't know until just before the German rule fell apart and we were about to be liberated and we could hear the guns of the front coming close.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- I didn't even know that he existed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he didn't know about me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Professor 'Zirnofsky,' Zirnauskas, professor of chemistry, very talented.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He did not want to go to Palestine or to Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He died a few years ago.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a professor of chemistry at the Vilnius University.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was the dean of, actually, chemistry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Zirnauskas, Z-I-R-N-A-U-S-K-A-S.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember his first name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He sent me to-- to one farmer.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
